('62c6645184267', 'Universitas Multimedia Nusantara', 'universitas-multimedia-nusantara', 'Universitas Multimedia Nusantara (UMN) is one of ICT-based universities that has a vision to become a country’s leading university.', '<p>Universitas Multimedia Nusantara (UMN) is one of ICT-based universities that has a vision to become a country&rsquo;s leading university.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/62c6645184267.png\" style=\"height:auto; width:50%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located in Gading Serpong, Tangerang, UMN has a new eco green tower to support students&rsquo; academic life. We&rsquo;re committed to deliver highly competent graduates with good character and technopreneurship skills, so we invite highly qualified candidates to join us in any position that we provide here. UMN becomes an outstanding university in ICT at both national and international levels, which produces graduates that are internationally-minded and highly competent in their field equipped with an entrepreneurial spirit and noble character.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'UMN,partner', 10, 12, 2, 'draft', '62c6645184267.png', '2022-07-07 12:42:57', '2022-08-18 01:59:02', 12),
